        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "埃米爾露出十分甜蜜的微笑",
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "這些對我來說，都是最浪漫的事喲？",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "甜言蜜語也好，驚喜也好，沒有一顆真正為對方著想的心，就只是空洞的話語，和俗套的行為",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "而只有了解了一個人想要些什麼，才能走進每個人的內心。",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "我會喜歡指揮官，也是因為指揮官知道我想要什麼，並把它給了我",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_school"
    },
    {
      "say": "能遇到指揮官實在是太好了呢~",
      "actor": 802010,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
